                            </p>
<div class="impact-metrics" style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
<div class="metric-item">
<span class="metric-val" style="color:white;">40.900+</span>
<span class="metric-label" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">Member Aktif</span>
</div>
<div class="metric-item">
<span class="metric-val" style="color:white;">50+</span>
